What you need to know:  The winner will be declared during the 19th edition of Sports Personality of the Year (SOYA) Gala on January 20 this year at Kenyatta International Convention Centre (KICC)Wawira will battle Paralympian Nancy Chelagat and Deaflympics athletics trio of Beryl Wamira, Linnet Nanjala and Serah Wangari for the coveted awardWawira was the only person outside athletics to win a medal for Kenya at the Commonwealth Games held July 28 to August 9, last year in Birmingham, England